  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK172">
<l>paṭupayaṉ veḵkip paḻippaṭava ceyyār</l>
<l>naṭuvaṉmai nāṇu pavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who blush at the want of equity will not commit disgraceful acts through desire of the profit that may be gained.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
